data.title: Jean Louis Prevost (1760-1810)
data.meta_description: Collection des Fleurs et des Fruits Paris, 1805 Stipple engravings with original hand-coloring. These exquisite engravings, from the 1805 “Collection des Fleurs et des Fruits”, present Prévost's mastery both of decorative design and descriptive rigor. This edition of the “Collection”, lauded as one of the greatest earl
